videos.description: D'Eriq King picks up his 10th rushing touchdown of the season with a 47-yard run to give Houston an early 7-0 lead over South Florida.
videos.headline: Houston strikes first with 47-yd TD run

videos.description: Marquez Stevenson takes the ball out of the air on a pass from D'Eriq King and runs into the end zone for a 15-yard Houston touchdown.
videos.headline: Stevenson snatches 15-yard TD

videos.description: Jordan Cronkrite walks into the end zone to get the Bulls on the board.
videos.headline: South Florida gets on board with short TD

videos.description: Johnny Ford gets South Florida back in the game with a 32-yard touchdown run, tying the score at 14.
videos.headline: Ford evens the score with 32-yd TD

videos.description: D'Eriq King connects with Marquez Stevenson for a 38-yard Cougars touchdown.
videos.headline: Houston answers with 38-yd TD pass

videos.description: Johnny Ford picks up his second touchdown run of the game to tie South Florida's matchup with Houston.
videos.headline: South Florida continues to rally with game-tying TD run

videos.description: The Cougars re-take the lead on a 30-yard touchdown pass from D'Eriq King to Courtney Lark.
videos.headline: King connects with Lark for 30-yd Houston TD

videos.description: D'Eriq King weaves through South Florida's defense for a 36-yard Houston touchdown.
videos.headline: King finds gap for 36-yard TD run

videos.description: D'Eriq King finds Jeremy Singleton, who runs 52 yards into the end zone, giving Houston a comfortable 41-29 lead over South Florida.
videos.headline: King and Singleton connect to widen Houston's lead

videos.description: Blake Barnett throws deep to DeAngelo Antoine for a 39-yard touchdown for the Bulls.
videos.headline: Barnett finds Antoine for 39-yd USF TD

videos.description: Houston's Mulbah Car runs into the end zone for an 11-yard Houston touchdown, giving the Cougars a 14-point lead over the Bulls.
videos.headline: Houston continues to cruise with 11-yd TD run

videos.description: D'Eriq King connects with Raelon Singleton for a 27-yard Cougars touchdown.
videos.headline: Houston keeps piling on with 27-yard TD pass
